<Layout 
	title="Portfolio de Jorge Borja - Analista de Datos"
	description="Analista de datos con +3 años de experiencia, conocimientos avanzados en matemática y estadística. Ofrece servicios de análisis de la información, ciencia de datos y desarrollo de aplicaciones visuales."
>
	<main class="sm:!py-7">
		<section class="w-full lg:w-[740px] mx-auto py-60 h-screen z-1">
			<h2 class="text-[#9d4edd] text-center text-4xl animationn font-semibold">Data Analyst</h2>
			<h1 class="text-center text-7xl font-bold">Jorge Borja Serrano</h1>
			<span class="flex justify-center text-gray-500 mt-2">Data's Storyteller, Insight's Architect.</span>

			<nav class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 mt-3 justify-center">
				<Pills href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jorgeborjas25/">
					<LinkedIn class="size-5"/>
					LinkedIn
				</Pills>
				<Pills href="https://github.com/unfresh25">
					<Github class="size-5"/>
					Github
				</Pills>
				<Pills href="https://uninorte-my.sharepoint.com/personal/jborjaa_uninorte_edu_co/_layouts/15/download.aspx?SourceUrl=%2Fpersonal%2Fjborjaa%5Funinorte%5Fedu%5Fco%2FDocuments%2FDocumentos%2FDocumentos%20laborales%2FJorge%20Borja%2C%20Curriculum%20Vitae%2Epdf">
					<Download class="size-5"/>
					Curriculum
				</Pills>
				<Pills href="mailto:jorgeborja48@gmail.com">
					<Email class="size-5"/>
					jorgeborja48@gmail.com
				</Pills>
			</nav>
		</section>
		<section class="flex justify-center w-full lg:w-[1140px] h-screen mx-auto text-animation z-1 mt-14" id="about">
			<h1 class="text-center !text-5xl lg:!text-9xl mx-auto z-[-1] opacity-60 font-black lg:-mt-16 section-title">ABOUT ME</h1>
			<p class="!text-xl lg:!text-5xl text-pretty reveal-text font-semibold m-4 lg:m-0 mt-28">
				Data analyst with <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">+3 years of experience</span> in data analysis and interpretation. 
				Strong foundation in <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">mathematics and statistics</span>, with a passion for theoretical 
				concepts and their practical applications. Adept at leveraging statistical techniques and data visualization tools to 
				drive <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">insights</span> and support <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">decision-making</span> 
				processes. 
			</p>
		</section>
		<section class="relative flex justify-center flex-col items-center timeline m-4 lg:m-auto" id="experience">
			<h1 class="text-center !text-5xl lg:!text-9xl mx-auto z-[-1] opacity-60 font-black section-title">EXPERIENCE</h1>
			<article class="lg:mt-[-120px]">
				<div class="relative flex flex-col items-center" style="flex-flow: column;">
					<div class="absolute w-1 h-0 bg-[#9d4edd] z-[-1] line-timeline" />
					<div 
						class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 w-full ml-auto mr-auto pt-20 pb-20 opacity-10 timeline-text-k" 
						style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 160px 1fr;"
					>
						<div>
							<span class="font-medium !text-base lg:!text-5xl">
								September, 2023
							</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-center size-4 bg-white rounded-full m-auto ball-k" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="font-medium !text-xs lg:!text-xl text-pretty exp-p">
								Started working at <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">Komatsu Colombia S.A.S.</span> as the principal data analyst,
								responsible for <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">centralizing data</span> from over 100 databases,
								creating <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">automation workflows</span> in Azure Data Factory, and developing
								projects such as an inventory demand <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">forecasting</span> application,
								<span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">Monte Carlo simulations</span> for machine working hours, work order 
								<span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">automation</span>, predictions for <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">service 
								offerings</span>, and creating elegant <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">Power BI reports</span>.
							</p>														
						</div>
					</div>
					<div 
						class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 w-full ml-auto mr-auto pt-20 pb-20 opacity-10 timeline-text-ur" 
						style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 160px 1fr"
					>
						<div>
							<span class="font-medium !text-base lg:!text-5xl">
								August, 2021
							</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-center size-4 bg-white rounded-full m-auto ball-ur" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="font-medium !text-xs lg:!text-xl text-pretty exp-p">
								Started working at <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">Urbefuturo</span> as a programmer data analyst, responsible for 
								the <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">implementation of statistical methods</span> for data analysis and 
								<span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">restructuring</span> of the database. Creation of <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">reports 
								and data visualization</span> using Power BI. Implementation of <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">geolocation</span> to 
								keep control of the surveys and, consequently, implementation of predictive models to find the most 
								<span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">optimal locations</span> for conducting the surveys.
							</p>														
						</div>
					</div>
					<div 
						class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 w-full ml-auto mr-auto pt-20 pb-20 opacity-10 timeline-text-phd" 
						style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 160px 1fr"
					>
						<div>
							<span class="font-medium !text-base lg:!text-5xl">
								April, 2023 - May - 2023
							</span>
						</div>
						<div>
							<div class="flex justify-center size-4 bg-white rounded-full m-auto ball-phd" />
						</div>
						<div>
							<p class="font-medium !text-xs lg:!text-xl text-pretty exp-p">
								Advisor for <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">PhD thesis in mathematics</span>. Translation of existing codes to create 
								<span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">optimizations and implement</span> new analysis methods. Created <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">simulation 
								of SPH</span> to understand its behavior in different scenarios and in different quantities. <span class="text-[#9d4edd] font-bold">Improvement</span> 
								of the obtained mathematical calculations and conversion to code.
							</p>														
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
		</section>
